<L>__{interior lobby (dusk) semi long shot}
<A>__{we see ben ascending the stairs originally taken by the dignitary and his group.}
<L>__{interior upstairs corridor (dusk) semi long shot}
<A>__{ben comes into the corridor and looks about him. beyond him we see a group of men obviously detectives, and ahead of them a police constable. we see ben hurry in his direction.}
<L>__{interior upstairs corridor (dusk) semi long shot}
<A>__{ben comes up to the constable and is about to pass him when he is stopped. we again do not hear the dialogue, but the pantomime shows that ben is trying to get to buchanan. the constable doesn't quite know what to make of ben's dramatic plea. he indicates that he must talk to his superior. ben waits impatiently as the constable goes over to one of the inspectors who is standing in a small group a little way off. from his viewpoint we see the constable addressing the inspector with skeptical nods of his head in ben's direction.}
